item.description:
Hello Everyone,

Larches Inn will hold a book club gathering on Jan.14th at 7:00. Hope everyone read the Great book Lisa chose for us! I can't wait to hear what everyone's reveiws are. For all our new members that would like to attend this would be a perfect time, because we will choose a new book at this meet up.This is a free gathering but we ask everyone to bring something light and refreshing to snack on.
Hope to see everyone soon, (Rain thought she would be away until Thursday but she will be here on Wed, so since everyone is having a problem making Thursday meet up I change it back to Wed)
Sue
